name: Spiked Magazine - Issue 6 Ft.Fluidity
description:
Issue 6 of Spiked Magazine, with a big feature on Fluidity from the Spiked Road Trip To Wales.

"SPIKED Edition 6 – Aug – Nov 2010
Edition 6 of the worldwide parkour and action sports magazine is out on 25th August.  This edition will cover multi sports action but have a big focus on women in sport. This edition will feature one of the leading ladies within the parkour community, our very own Annty Marais. This edition will also be featuring some of the most influential women from the world of muay thai boxing and MMA, Karen '9mm' Ousey and Rosi Sexton. Plus more in-depth articles from the parkour community, some fantastic photography and much more.  Including an exclusive lowdown on the biggest action sports event to hit the UK - SPIKED X in the City."
